Loggly,is,a,cloud,based,logging,service,with,tools,for,collecting,data,in,any,format,searching,data,easily,and,accessing,data,analytics,Loggly,also,provides,a,RESTful,API,for,developers,to,create,their,own,applications,around,the,Loggly,services,Developers,can,send,events,to,Loggly,retrieve,events,and,access,inputs,and,devices,Loggly,is,currently,in,Beta,stage